{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"go","postPath":"go-for","post":{"title":"Go: for 语句","body":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_for_语句\">for 语句</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_for_语句\">for 语句</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>Go 语言只有一种循环语句：<code>for</code> 循环。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>像 Java、C 或 JavaScript 那样，基本的 <code>for</code> 循环有三个部分，用两个分号隔开，其中：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>第一部分是初始化语句，只在 <code>for</code> 循环开始时执行一次。这一部分应该是一个短变量声明，而且这里声明的变量仅在 <code>for</code> 语句作用域内可用。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>第二部分是条件表达式，如果值为 <code>True</code> 就会迭代。一旦值为 <code>False</code>，循环就会结束。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>第三部分是迭代后语句，在每次迭代后执行。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>和 Java、C 或 JavaScript 不同的是，<code>for</code> 循环中的三个部分没有被括号括起来，而且 <code>for</code> 循环后面的花括号不可省略。举个例子：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\">sum := <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> i := <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>; i++ {\n    sum += i\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><code>for</code> 语句的初始化语句和迭代后语句可以省略，如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\">sum := <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> ; sum &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span>; {\n    sum += sum\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><code>for</code> 循环甚至可以像 C 语言中的 <code>while</code> 那样使用，如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\">sum := <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> sum &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span> {\n    sum += sum\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>如果你连条件表达式都省了，那么 <code>for</code> 语句就会无限循环，如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// do something forever</span>\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>Go 没有逗号操作符，而且 <code>++</code> 和 <code>--</code> 是语句而非表达式，所以，如果要在 <code>for</code> 语句中使用多个变量，应使用平行命名的方式：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 反转 a</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> i, j := <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(a)<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>; i &lt; j; i, j = i+<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, j<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span> {\n\ta[i], a[j] = a[j], a[i]\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"Go 基础","toc":[{"title":"基础","path":"go-basic"},{"title":"函数","path":"go-func"},{"title":"变量","path":"go-var"},{"title":"基本类型","path":"go-basic-types"},{"title":"字符串","path":"go-string"},{"title":"指针","path":"go-ptr"},{"title":"数组和切片","path":"go-array-slice"},{"title":"映射","path":"go-map"},{"title":"结构：struct","path":"go-struct"},{"title":"接口：interface","path":"go-itf"},{"title":"type 关键字","path":"go-type"},{"title":"for 语句","path":"go-for"},{"title":"if 语句","path":"go-if"},{"title":"switch 语句","path":"go-switch"},{"title":"defer 语句","path":"go-defer"},{"title":"并发","path":"go-concurrency"},{"title":"包和导入","path":"go-pkg-import"}],"path":"go"}},"__N_SSG":true}